# **Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic – Description**

I created my digital literacy awareness infographic using Canva, a free and easy-to-use online design tool. The infographic covers 
important topics such as what digital literacy is, useful digital tools for students, safe internet practices, and professional online presence. 
I used a blue color theme along with simple icons and clear headings to make the design visually appealing and easy to understand.

This highlights how digital literacy helps students use technology effectively, stay safe online, and build a positive digital identity.

